#. Description of the theme
msgid ""
"Elmira is a free, multipurpose WordPress theme engineered for large "
"enterprises and ambitious businesses demanding outstanding functionality and "
"pixel-perfect design. Its signature dark, proficient layout and refined "
"color scheme immediately establish a sense of professionalism and authority. "
"It is perfectly suited for: Business, Corporate, Finance, Agency, Consulting,"
" SaaS, Education, Construction, eCommerce (WooCommerce), Health &amp; "
"Medical, Law, Architecture, industries, Blog/Magazine, Fashion, Online Shop, "
"Travel, and more. It has some exotic features like clean code, advanced "
"typography, sticky menu, logo upload, header image, Bootstrap 4 framework, "
"built with SEO in mind, mobile-ready, translation-ready (WPML, Polylang), "
"and built to be beautiful on all screen sizes. This theme supports the best "
"Elementor page builder to create, edit, and update page designs as per the "
"requirement. Elmira also supports popular free and premium WordPress plugins,"
" including Elementor, Yoast SEO, WooCommerce, Contact Form 7, Jetpack, "
"Google Analytics, and more. Check the demo of ArileWP Pro https://themearile."
"com/arilewp-pro-theme/."
msgstr ""

